{"tid":2033854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分化撚最新手段: 分化BNO持有人","createTime":"2020-05-25T01:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:04:20.000Z","uid":13543,"like":87,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"dc973cd7a827faf671b8fc6b76c7261b39ba6a75","tid":2033854,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:58:38.000Z","msg":"咁多人幫手要引起外國關注<br />\n今日有少少新聞就即刻一大班人吹風話好驚有BNO既人會自私走左去<br />\n根本得2個可能:<br />\n1) 冇BNO既妒忌撚<br />\n呢班人連不分化都唔識講<br />\n仲有你以為話走就走?<br />\n唔洗PLAN?<br />\n<br />\n2) 5毛分化撚<br />\n想令我地停止爭取外國關注同支持<br />\n都係要全家死絕既賤種"},{"pid":"8554d22e77c20f74cdcd47adbc3a6255de217ceb","tid":2033854,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e08652dc8768367399afdc08962f1e694bb6cd","tid":2033854,"uid":13724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:03:29.000Z","msg":"嗰班人本質上同嗌不要讓李家誠跑了嘅小粉紅一樣"},{"pid":"5728cbb52888de12edfc48e4ad582d3f418a5c69","tid":2033854,"uid":146797,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:09:40.000Z","msg":"巴打走先<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔會幫你頂"},{"pid":"8610586cc11532c24a4df058c316b03d763ee1f1","tid":2033854,"uid":205043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:13:12.000Z","msg":"d冇既小學雞講撚到平左權=可以輕鬆即刻走咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7447096cd3afb4bad7108ae3c1f3cb69ab292515","tid":2033854,"uid":13543,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8610586cc11532c24a4df058c316b03d763ee1f1","tid":2033854,"uid":205043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:13:12.000Z","msg":"d冇既小學雞講撚到平左權=可以輕鬆即刻走咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:15:13.000Z","msg":"爭取左外國關注同支持咁耐<br />\n而家先話反對同擔心<br />\n其實佢地冇諗過要爭取到D乜野<br />\n只係諗住要死一齊死"},{"pid":"a4888a2db554576fdcd01645f3bde01ea3f29bd6","tid":2033854,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8610586cc11532c24a4df058c316b03d763ee1f1","tid":2033854,"uid":205043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:13:12.000Z","msg":"d冇既小學雞講撚到平左權=可以輕鬆即刻走咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"佢地應該共享支那人榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a126106190ba5590d3b6c834d24030c946abb5","tid":2033854,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7844f3d43fd21740b067852dc106d07dcd24dae7","tid":2033854,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5ef9142f6c14d6fc039fe25bbfe1cbc7282196","tid":2033854,"uid":87735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:23:19.000Z","msg":"救得一個得一個"},{"pid":"2998c0d460a4c629be7390db5195eb504b6c015d","tid":2033854,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2504073c664497494b330d82e510fa6af590fc","tid":2033854,"uid":81151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34cb37d8630f1b2426dd2c5999131fe47f61f909","tid":2033854,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"d1280b0e658aba682f40ee3a20e8e942f419c6ef","tid":2033854,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3ceb7452c005a0f861e10b270ad99c344c6d5e","tid":2033854,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:10:16.000Z","msg":"好多分化撚借題發揮"},{"pid":"03bc8bdaa71dfbd0894b27e9f5b2e2873414e991","tid":2033854,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8610586cc11532c24a4df058c316b03d763ee1f1","tid":2033854,"uid":205043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T02:13:12.000Z","msg":"d冇既小學雞講撚到平左權=可以輕鬆即刻走咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"尋日我都比5毛圍攻"},{"pid":"fd00d2c9e22a02d2d05d72b07e274600a014252a","tid":2033854,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a3ceb7452c005a0f861e10b270ad99c344c6d5e","tid":2033854,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:10:16.000Z","msg":"好多分化撚借題發揮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"呢個話題好惹火<br />\n唔怪之我比5毛圍攻"},{"pid":"b93b757d87a6336565940d7671c7b850141894f3","tid":2033854,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"BNO呢單嘢根本完全唔值得討論<br />\n<br />\n首先根本就唔會出現所謂BNO平權<br />\n有嘅最多都係變種專才引入計劃<br />\n英國自身難保再引啲窮人老人入去做蝗蟲<br />\n就算政府唔趕 出街都分分鍾畀人打<br />\n成日講英國有道義責任無意思<br />\n佢地根本無道義可言<br />\n<br />\n其次搵後路呢件事無一個人唔係做緊<br />\n喺前線嘅都一樣要有逃生門<br />\n準備好逃生門之後幾時逃生去到幾盡係個人意志問題<br />\n你要唔畀人走 同屌啲潛咗出境避難嘅手足無乜分別<br />\n<br />\n大家亦太睇少國際線上嘅手足<br />\n有幾多人身在外地支持今次抗爭自己數下<br />\n認為拎到個居留權就等如出賣香港未免太對唔住呢班手足"},{"pid":"f9a13dce691d9ca69edb0ea4da744746034ac939","tid":2033854,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93b757d87a6336565940d7671c7b850141894f3","tid":2033854,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"BNO呢單嘢根本完全唔值得討論<br />\n<br />\n首先根本就唔會出現所謂BNO平權<br />\n有嘅最多都係變種專才引入計劃<br />\n英國自身難保再引啲窮人老人入去做蝗蟲<br />\n就算政府唔趕 出街都分分鍾畀人打<br />\n成日講英國有道義責任無意思<br />\n佢地根本無道義可言<br />\n<br />\n其次搵後路呢件事無一個人唔係做緊<br />\n喺前線嘅都一樣要有逃生門<br />\n準備好逃生門之後幾時逃生去到幾盡係個人意志問題<br />\n你要唔畀人走 同屌啲潛咗出境避難嘅手足無乜分別<br />\n<br />\n大家亦太睇少國際線上嘅手足<br />\n有幾多人身在外地支持今次抗爭自己數下<br />\n認為拎到個居留權就等如出賣香港未免太對唔住呢班手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:39:22.000Z","msg":"其實有bc都做唔到蝗蟲，唔好當做香港個制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有bc但冇做野冇交返幾年稅都未有福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85321546d18156663108b3280d0304e28a4ad02c","tid":2033854,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:40:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f01183910137a33755ce17c93f011447e76bbc9d","tid":2033854,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f9a13dce691d9ca69edb0ea4da744746034ac939","tid":2033854,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93b757d87a6336565940d7671c7b850141894f3","tid":2033854,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"BNO呢單嘢根本完全唔值得討論<br />\n<br />\n首先根本就唔會出現所謂BNO平權<br />\n有嘅最多都係變種專才引入計劃<br />\n英國自身難保再引啲窮人老人入去做蝗蟲<br />\n就算政府唔趕 出街都分分鍾畀人打<br